==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|godsib|lang=enm}}, {{term|gossib||close friend that one likes to talk to|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|godsibb|lang=ang||godparent}}, from {{term|god|lang=ang}} + {{term|sibb||kinsman|lang=ang}} (compare [[sibling]]).

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# Someone who likes to talk about someone else’s private or personal business.
# Idle [[talk]] about someone’s [[private]] or [[personal]] matters, especially someone not present.

